    "Finally, the relational norms model was better at predicting such moral judgments than other common ways of characterizing relationships in the literature, such as by genetic relatedness, social closeness, or interdependence [19,21].",
    "Relational norms in human-AI relationshipsHuman-human relational norms may not straightforwardly map onto human relationships with AI for several reasons.",
